::DrillBit::

"There isn't a thing wrong, love. I'm just so happy to see you. I
thought we would never be together again."
He leaned over giving her a kiss.
"So what are you planing on doing now? Take back command?"
It took him a second, but he suddenly relized what that would mean.
He was the Commander, was this the end of that? But he decided that he
would rather have KitKat then Command.
